"Nice to meet you Gigatron."  She walked back to Chordate and took 
his arm. She smiled at smiled at both bots and looked towards the 
hatch,"Shall we?" She motioned with her tail.  "I was going with 
Chordate for a walk outside. If you two have buisness, I can wait or 
walk outside alone? I just don't want to be in the way." She said in 
a soft, sweet voice.
